#

Filet Mignon with Garlic Herb Butter and Parmesan Risotto

$75
850 kcal
Difficulty: 80%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten Free

Tags:

GourmetSteakRisottoDinner

Description

Tender filet mignon topped with a rich garlic herb butter, served alongside a creamy and savory Parmesan risotto.

Ingredients

  • Filet Mignon: 4 (6 oz each)
  • Unsalted Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Fresh Parsley: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tbsp, chopped
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Arborio Rice: 1 cup
  • Chicken Broth: 4 cups
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Shallot: 1, finely chopped
  • Dry White Wine: 1/2 cup
  • Heavy Cream: 1/4 cup
